rcase\n  41→- Registry stores normalized command names\n  42→\n  43→DECISIONS:\n  44→- 2026-03-12 | F-002-bot-commands | Add command routing layer with parser, registry, validator for pipeline commands\n  45→- 2026-03-12 | F-002-alias-mapping | Support command aliases /p, /b, /s, /l\n  46→"}],"is_error":false}],"role":"user"},"parent_tool_use_id":"019cde4f5e78286f786a1f91fc1d6806","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T19:11:10.342Z","_requestId":"4b990aef1ee94c0d9951653ca0a8a1f1"}
